00:43:37.950 --> 00:43:40.780
the majority of the returns came
from a handful of businesses.

00:43:40.780 --> 00:43:44.390
American Express in the
'60s, and then See's

00:43:44.390 --> 00:43:48.142
Candies, Coca-Cola,
American Express again.

00:43:48.142 --> 00:43:52.410
And primarily the
reason being that he

00:43:52.410 --> 00:43:55.410
had a very concentrated bet.

00:43:55.410 --> 00:43:58.350
American Express
was some 30%, 40%,

00:43:58.350 --> 00:44:03.720
and Coke was, I think,
over 20% of the capital.

00:44:03.720 --> 00:44:07.360
And GEICO also was a
pretty significant bet.

00:44:07.360 --> 00:44:10.880
So when he made
these investments,

00:44:10.880 --> 00:44:14.390
they were out of favor, and
he had a differentiated view.

00:44:14.390 --> 00:44:18.670
And the differentiated view
came from he doing scuttlebutt

00:44:18.670 --> 00:44:21.810
on these companies that
gave him these kind

00:44:21.810 --> 00:44:23.390
of differentiated point of view.

00:44:23.390 --> 00:44:25.690
You know, the security
I like the best,

00:44:25.690 --> 00:44:27.400
and American Express
he went around

00:44:27.400 --> 00:44:28.780
and did all the scuttlebutt.

00:44:28.780 --> 00:44:33.170
So my point being is,
from those lessons,

00:44:33.170 --> 00:44:35.940
seems like concentration,
scuttlebutt,

00:44:35.940 --> 00:44:39.136
if I am going to be a stock
picker, are important.

00:44:39.136 --> 00:44:41.520
What are lessons
from there that we

00:44:41.520 --> 00:44:44.750
can do today apply if I am
an active investing picking

00:44:44.750 --> 00:44:48.526
stocks, and I-- if
concentrated is the way to go?

00:44:48.526 --> 00:44:50.830
The counter-- just to
complete the sentence-- is,

00:44:50.830 --> 00:44:53.940
the counter being
lots of hedge funds

00:44:53.940 --> 00:44:56.430
thought that they had a
differentiated point of view,

00:44:56.430 --> 00:44:57.910
and they were all in Valeant.

00:44:57.910 --> 00:44:59.680
And it was a concentrated bet.

00:44:59.680 --> 00:45:02.450
It could always go
the other way and kill

00:45:02.450 --> 00:45:04.420
