So Sequoia Funds, right?

00:45:09.550 --> 00:45:11.360
Taken down,
effectively, reputation

00:45:11.360 --> 00:45:13.980
was dismantled by
Valeant, was created

00:45:13.980 --> 00:45:16.890
because Buffett's
partnership closed.

00:45:16.890 --> 00:45:19.224
The investors who wanted
to maintain their exposure

00:45:19.224 --> 00:45:21.640
to the equity market, even
though Buffett was recommending

00:45:21.640 --> 00:45:24.930
that they didn't do that,
he gave them the option.

00:45:24.930 --> 00:45:26.730
Bill Ruane was there.

00:45:26.730 --> 00:45:32.250
Started Sequoia for
the partnership,

00:45:32.250 --> 00:45:35.310
so that people who
