00:45:46.470 --> 00:45:48.810
It improves the returns.

00:45:48.810 --> 00:45:52.060
Your question sort of
framed it very well.

00:45:52.060 --> 00:45:53.980
Part of the reason
for the success

00:45:53.980 --> 00:45:58.380
was he was concentrated
in the right stuff.

00:45:58.380 --> 00:45:59.610
Right?

00:45:59.610 --> 00:46:04.520
Part of the reason for the
downfall of the Sequoia Funds

00:46:04.520 --> 00:46:07.390
was that they were concentrated
in the wrong stuff.

00:46:07.390 --> 00:46:08.470
Right?

00:46:08.470 --> 00:46:14.180
So it works really well as long
as you don't make a mistake,

00:46:14.180 --> 00:46:15.130
I guess is the point.

00:46:15.130 --> 00:46:21.190
So the degree to which you have
the confidence in what you're

00:46:21.190 --> 00:46:24.760
doing should determine the
degree of concentration

00:46:24.760 --> 00:46:26.130
that you're willing to accept.

00:46:26.130 --> 00:46:27.630
Because if it goes
wrong, it's going

00:46:27.630 --> 00:46:29.590
to go horribly wrong
if you're concentrated,

00:46:29.590 --> 00:46:33.150
